snippet.title: Diana and Roma Water Balloons PlayDate with Baby Oliver
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma have a day off! The children had a Fun Day with inflatable toys and water balloons. Oliver also wants to play, but he is still small. Diana and Roma make a mini aqua park for baby Oliver and invite him to play date.
Thanks for watching!
